# 📡 API Documentation

## Base URL

```
/api/v1
```

---

# 🔐 Authentication

### ➤ Register

```
POST /user/register
```

### ➤ Login

```
POST /user/login
```

### ➤ Get Current User

```
GET /user/me
Authorization: Bearer <token>
```

---

# 👥 User Management (Admin)

### ➤ Get All Users

```
GET /user/users
```

### ➤ Get User by ID

```
GET /user/:userId
```

### ➤ Update Role

```
PATCH /user/:userId/role
```

### ➤ Deactivate User

```
DELETE /user/:userId
```

---

# 💸 Transactions

### ➤ Create Transaction

```
POST /transaction/create
```

### ➤ Get Transactions (Filters Supported)

```
GET /transaction
```

Query Params:

* page
* limit
* type
* category
* startDate
* endDate
* sort
* search

---

### ➤ Get Transaction by ID

```
GET /transaction/:transactionId
```

### ➤ Update Transaction

```
PATCH /transaction/update/:transactionId
```

### ➤ Delete Transaction

```
DELETE /transaction/:transactionId
```

---

# 📊 Dashboard

### ➤ Summary

```
GET /dashboard/summary
```

### ➤ Category Breakdown

```
GET /dashboard/category-breakdown
```

### ➤ Monthly Trends

```
GET /dashboard/monthly-trends
```

### ➤ Weekly Summary

```
GET /dashboard/weekly-summary
```

### ➤ Recent Activity

```
GET /dashboard/recent-activity
```

---

# 🔐 Authorization Rules

All protected routes require:

```
Authorization: Bearer <JWT_TOKEN>
```

---

# 🧠 Notes

* Soft delete implemented (`isDeleted`)
* Aggregation pipelines power analytics
* Pagination & filters supported
* Role-based access enforced
* Indexed queries for performance

---
